{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/LOGO_FIXED_copy-smaller.png?t=1737126750\" />In <i><strong>FAYE FALLING</strong></i> you play as a recently passed soul, unable to recall who they are, or how they died. After a chance encounter with a powerful entity, you begin <strong>an epic journey to defeat a growing darkness</strong>, while recovering your memories along the way...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/headings-COMBAT.png?t=1737126750\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/STEAM_FAYE_EVADE.gif?t=1737126750\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in fun, fast-paced <strong>turn-based battles</strong> against a large variety of enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Evade damage</strong> by dodging enemy attacks in quick, snappy minigames. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cast powerful spells</strong> to fight your opponents and protect yourself.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/headings-EXPLORATION.png?t=1737126750\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/STEAM_FAYE_EXPLORE.gif?t=1737126750\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Explore a diverse, ethereal world,</strong> filled with minigames, puzzles and secrets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete <strong>optional side quests</strong> to receive rare items and gear.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/headings_STORY.png?t=1737126750\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/STEAM_FATE_STORY.gif?t=1737126750\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lead a <strong>path of darkness</strong>, where you'll steal, kill and grow horns, <strong>or a path of light</strong>, where you'll spread hope and sprout a glowing halo.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet <strong>several strange characters</strong> along your journey; from an anxious skull, to a trio of divine angels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make significant narrative choices that'll lead you toward <strong>multiple endings</strong>. <i>(Including a hidden true ending.)</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unlock a New Game+</strong> mode with increased difficulty, and additional lore.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Faye Falling is an emotional gameplay experience that explores death, suffering and meaning.</i> It was made entirely by one person; me!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Numina I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1865750/6a524c003803d8521baff3dbbae4a8779be6a7d0.jpg"},{"name":"Numina II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1865750/6a524c003803d8521baff3dbbae4a8779be6a7d0.jpg"},{"name":"Numina III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1865750/6a524c003803d8521baff3dbbae4a8779be6a7d0.jpg"},{"name":"The Parasite","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1865750/6a524c003803d8521baff3dbbae4a8779be6a7d0.jpg"},{"name":"Ending 5: The True Ending","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1865750/9a43f1579e46807d25021e5970974cd5239312fd.jpg"},{"name":"The Shadow Armor","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1865750/6a524c003803d8521baff3db